PAR 5 INVESTMENT GROUP, Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
MERRIMACK MUTUAL FIRE INSURANCE COMPANY, Defendant-Respondent. C-893 September Term 2018
082528 Supreme Court of New Jersey. May 14, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001502-18 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
